criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  21 years of age or older;

          -  current Boston Medical Center patient - must have an upcoming returning patient
             appointment at Boston Medical Center or affiliated clinic within 3 months of
             recruitment;

          -  speaks English and/or Spanish.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Under 21 years of age;

          -  not a current patient of Boston Medical Center or affiliated clinic;

          -  unable to speak English and/or Spanish.
